1
00:01:10,000 --> 00:01:13,000
"Double Helix"

2
00:01:14,239 --> 00:01:15,799
The wedding is set to be held in Paris.

3
00:01:16,159 --> 00:01:17,239
You absolutely must come.

4
00:01:17,680 --> 00:01:18,720
Have you set the date yet?

5
00:01:19,200 --> 00:01:21,200
It should be finalized in
the next couple of days.

6
00:01:22,040 --> 00:01:23,560
But lately, Wen Shichen...

7
00:01:23,840 --> 00:01:25,600
seems to have developed
pre-wedding anxiety.

8
00:01:25,840 --> 00:01:26,640
Even though he doesn't say it,

9
00:01:26,641 --> 00:01:27,719
I can feel it.

10
00:01:27,840 --> 00:01:29,239
He's incredibly nervous.

11
00:01:29,480 --> 00:01:30,656
He's even worried you'll
come and steal me away.

12
00:01:30,680 --> 00:01:31,935
Then he really needs to watch out.

13
00:01:31,959 --> 00:01:33,919
I might actually crash
the wedding and steal you.

14
00:01:34,599 --> 00:01:35,799
I'd love nothing more.

15
00:01:37,680 --> 00:01:38,480
I have to go.

16
00:01:38,640 --> 00:01:40,016
He's coming over. Hanging up now. Bye!

17
00:01:40,040 --> 00:01:41,040
Okay.

18
00:01:42,799 --> 00:01:44,079
You're going to crash a wedding?

19
00:01:47,200 --> 00:01:48,959
Why do you walk so quietly?

20
00:01:49,480 --> 00:01:50,560
I was just joking.

21
00:01:51,599 --> 00:01:52,840
Do you think that's funny?

22
00:01:59,840 --> 00:02:00,959
What's wrong with you?

23
00:02:04,079 --> 00:02:05,079
Nothing.

24
00:02:06,680 --> 00:02:07,799
I'm going to take a shower.

25
00:02:22,599 --> 00:02:23,599
Well...

26
00:02:24,879 --> 00:02:26,319
Mr. Lu has some

27
00:02:26,520 --> 00:02:27,240
important matters to attend to lately.

28
00:02:27,319 --> 00:02:29,719
So it might not be very
convenient for you to stay here.

29
00:02:31,599 --> 00:02:32,599
Just...

30
00:02:37,919 --> 00:02:39,879
What's up with Mr. Lu
these past couple of days?

31
00:02:40,039 --> 00:02:41,919
He's even spacing out during meetings.

32
00:02:42,280 --> 00:02:44,160
Looks like he's
overindulging in his love life.

33
00:02:44,280 --> 00:02:45,400
Really?

34
00:02:45,479 --> 00:02:46,719
I saw it myself.

35
00:02:46,919 --> 00:02:48,119
These past few days,
he's been with that guy

36
00:02:48,120 --> 00:02:49,656
who used to come to
the office looking for him.

37
00:02:49,680 --> 00:02:51,360
They've been booking hotel rooms together.

38
00:02:51,879 --> 00:02:53,400
Did you go to the same hotel too?

39
00:02:53,520 --> 00:02:54,520
I...

40
00:02:57,300 --> 00:03:01,300
(Episode 12: Together for a Lifetime)

41
00:03:13,400 --> 00:03:16,319
I won't be going to work tomorrow.

42
00:03:17,479 --> 00:03:18,479
Why?

43
00:03:20,159 --> 00:03:21,520
You seem very busy,

44
00:03:22,039 --> 00:03:24,400
and I can't really help you with anything.

45
00:03:25,439 --> 00:03:27,039
I don't want to waste company resources.

46
00:03:29,159 --> 00:03:30,520
Tomorrow, I'll arrange for someone

47
00:03:30,759 --> 00:03:32,080
to have your desk moved back.

48
00:03:32,560 --> 00:03:33,240
No need.

49
00:03:33,479 --> 00:03:33,919
I...

50
00:03:34,000 --> 00:03:35,040
It'll be quick, I promise.

51
00:03:35,240 --> 00:03:36,720
It will definitely be moved tomorrow.

52
00:03:36,919 --> 00:03:38,639
So just go back to work like a good boy.

53
00:03:42,439 --> 00:03:44,280
Really, there's no need.

54
00:03:44,520 --> 00:03:46,599
Go ahead with your work. I want to go...

55
00:03:48,280 --> 00:03:49,280
Where do you want to go?

56
00:04:01,879 --> 00:04:02,879
I'm sorry.

57
00:04:04,439 --> 00:04:05,439
Go ahead and eat first.

58
00:04:06,680 --> 00:04:07,800
I'll go take a shower.

59
00:04:31,480 --> 00:04:32,720
I saw it myself.

60
00:04:32,959 --> 00:04:34,119
These past few days,
he's been with that guy

61
00:04:34,120 --> 00:04:35,656
who used to come to
the office looking for him.

62
00:04:35,680 --> 00:04:37,360
They've been booking hotel rooms together.

63
00:04:43,680 --> 00:04:45,560
Zhuo Lan's wedding
date is set for next month.

64
00:04:46,800 --> 00:04:48,639
I want to go there early.

65
00:04:51,480 --> 00:04:53,000
In what capacity are you going?

66
00:04:54,079 --> 00:04:55,639
Won't you feel embarrassed going there?

67
00:04:58,759 --> 00:05:00,040
How could you think that?

68
00:05:03,639 --> 00:05:05,039
How else do you expect me to think?

69
00:05:06,040 --> 00:05:07,399
You're her ex-husband.

70
00:05:10,199 --> 00:05:11,879
You know what our relationship is.

71
00:05:11,959 --> 00:05:13,079
We're just friends.

72
00:05:16,199 --> 00:05:17,199
Friends?

73
00:05:19,279 --> 00:05:20,480
I might believe that,

74
00:05:21,000 --> 00:05:22,160
but others won't.

75
00:05:26,319 --> 00:05:27,319
Lu Feng.

76
00:05:28,120 --> 00:05:29,280
What's wrong with you lately?

77
00:05:33,839 --> 00:05:35,000
Nothing is wrong with me.

78
00:05:35,800 --> 00:05:36,800
I'm fine.

79
00:05:36,959 --> 00:05:38,000
I've always been fine.

80
00:05:55,560 --> 00:05:56,959
Can you please not go to her?

81
00:05:58,560 --> 00:05:59,560
And after that,

82
00:06:00,240 --> 00:06:02,160
don't have any contact with her ever again.

83
00:06:04,560 --> 00:06:06,160
Lu Feng, you're hurting me.

84
00:06:09,800 --> 00:06:10,800
I'm sorry.

85
00:06:12,959 --> 00:06:14,519
What on earth is wrong with you lately?

86
00:06:15,800 --> 00:06:16,800
I'm fine.

87
00:06:18,639 --> 00:06:19,879
I've just been a bit busy.

88
00:06:31,639 --> 00:06:32,639
Busy?

89
00:06:33,480 --> 00:06:35,920
Do you still have time to book
hotel rooms with someone else?

90
00:06:38,519 --> 00:06:39,519
With whom?

91
00:06:41,240 --> 00:06:42,960
That guy from the restaurant the other day?

92
00:06:48,319 --> 00:06:49,759
Did you really book a room with him?

93
00:06:56,199 --> 00:06:57,199
Fine, let's do this.

94
00:06:58,399 --> 00:06:59,399
From now on,

95
00:07:00,199 --> 00:07:02,160
you can book rooms with whoever you want.

96
00:07:03,199 --> 00:07:05,000
If you're lonely and
want a lover, go ahead.

97
00:07:05,279 --> 00:07:06,799
Even if you get married, I don't care.

98
00:07:07,199 --> 00:07:08,560
Do whatever you want.

99
00:07:10,959 --> 00:07:12,919
What do you mean you
don't care if I get married?

100
00:07:12,959 --> 00:07:14,759
What do you mean
it's fine if I find a lover?

101
00:07:15,839 --> 00:07:17,439
Do you really care about me that little?

102
00:07:25,160 --> 00:07:26,160
I'm sorry, Xiao Chen.

103
00:07:26,399 --> 00:07:27,480
I didn't mean to.

104
00:07:40,639 --> 00:07:42,240
Are you really going to see Zhuo Lan?

105
00:07:48,040 --> 00:07:49,040
I don't agree to it.

106
00:07:54,399 --> 00:07:55,839
You booked a room with someone else.

107
00:07:56,759 --> 00:07:57,759
Did I agree to that?

108
00:08:06,319 --> 00:08:07,319
He's a doctor.

109
00:08:08,600 --> 00:08:09,720
A psychiatrist.

110
00:08:13,600 --> 00:08:15,399
I'm really worried he'll leave me.

111
00:08:19,639 --> 00:08:22,279
Back then, when his mother wanted
him to break up with me, he did.

112
00:08:23,920 --> 00:08:26,000
Now, when his brother
tells him to leave, he leaves.

113
00:08:26,040 --> 00:08:27,656
When his ex-wife tells
him to leave, he leaves.

114
00:08:27,680 --> 00:08:29,600
He'll leave if anyone tells him to.

115
00:08:33,200 --> 00:08:34,720
I'm really afraid that one day,

116
00:08:36,919 --> 00:08:38,240
he'll suddenly walk away

117
00:08:41,440 --> 00:08:42,799
and never come back.

118
00:08:45,080 --> 00:08:46,936
Go to the hospital for a
comprehensive checkup.

119
00:08:46,960 --> 00:08:47,960
See a psychiatrist.

120
00:08:48,360 --> 00:08:49,360
That's impossible.

121
00:08:49,519 --> 00:08:50,799
I can't be sick.

122
00:08:52,000 --> 00:08:53,320
His name is Zhao Chi.

123
00:08:55,200 --> 00:08:56,559
My sister introduced him to me.

124
00:09:00,000 --> 00:09:01,080
Over the past few years,

125
00:09:01,840 --> 00:09:04,000
whenever my emotions got unstable,

126
00:09:05,440 --> 00:09:07,000
I would go to him for counseling.

127
00:09:09,639 --> 00:09:10,639
He said

128
00:09:12,799 --> 00:09:14,639
I have bipolar disorder

129
00:09:15,759 --> 00:09:17,439
and kept telling me to go to the hospital.

130
00:09:19,200 --> 00:09:20,440
I was too afraid to go.

131
00:09:21,200 --> 00:09:22,240
Why didn't you go?

132
00:09:22,480 --> 00:09:24,720
How could I have a mood disorder?

133
00:09:29,200 --> 00:09:30,399
I love you so much.

134
00:09:32,159 --> 00:09:33,159
I was afraid.

135
00:09:34,080 --> 00:09:35,480
If I'm really sick,

136
00:09:36,840 --> 00:09:38,480
you'll want me even less.

137
00:09:39,320 --> 00:09:40,320
I was afraid

138
00:09:41,279 --> 00:09:42,799
you'd think my love for you

139
00:09:44,320 --> 00:09:46,480
was just because of my illness,

140
00:09:47,426 --> 00:09:48,466
and not real.

141
00:09:50,360 --> 00:09:51,720
Don't listen to his nonsense.

142
00:09:52,919 --> 00:09:54,240
Whether you love me or not,

143
00:09:54,720 --> 00:09:56,000
how could I not know?

144
00:09:56,840 --> 00:09:57,840
It's not fake.

145
00:10:00,720 --> 00:10:01,720
Really?

146
00:10:59,449 --> 00:11:01,223
[Zhao Chi's contact infomration]

147
00:11:04,480 --> 00:11:05,480
Hello.

148
00:11:06,200 --> 00:11:07,200
I'm Cheng Yichen.

149
00:11:08,320 --> 00:11:09,480
Can we meet?

150
00:11:53,399 --> 00:11:54,399
You're awake.

151
00:11:54,919 --> 00:11:56,240
Go freshen up and have breakfast.

152
00:11:56,679 --> 00:11:58,439
Chou Cheng will be
here to pick you up soon.

153
00:11:58,600 --> 00:11:59,600
Today,

154
00:11:59,759 --> 00:12:01,879
you have a very important
meeting to attend.

155
00:12:03,440 --> 00:12:05,159
Can't you come with me?

156
00:12:05,559 --> 00:12:06,559
No.

157
00:12:06,879 --> 00:12:08,440
Look at what a mess the house is.

158
00:12:08,679 --> 00:12:10,439
I've called a cleaning
service to come over.

159
00:12:13,039 --> 00:12:14,039
Don't worry.

160
00:12:14,360 --> 00:12:15,399
I won't leave.

161
00:12:16,039 --> 00:12:17,799
If you're really that worried,

162
00:12:18,159 --> 00:12:20,480
my passport and ID are in the drawer.

163
00:12:20,639 --> 00:12:21,799
You can take them with you.

164
00:12:22,519 --> 00:12:24,559
Just focus on your meeting today.

165
00:12:25,120 --> 00:12:26,120
About Zhao Chi,

166
00:12:26,440 --> 00:12:27,600
we'll talk when you get back.

167
00:12:27,639 --> 00:12:28,639
Okay?

168
00:12:46,600 --> 00:12:48,000
Go to work and do a good job today.

169
00:12:48,080 --> 00:12:49,080
Don't overthink things.

170
00:13:14,600 --> 00:13:15,600
Go on.

171
00:13:27,159 --> 00:13:28,159
Go on.

172
00:13:28,480 --> 00:13:29,480
I'll be waiting for you.

173
00:13:52,519 --> 00:13:53,519
Doing this...

174
00:13:53,720 --> 00:13:55,480
doesn't that violate patient privacy?

175
00:13:56,840 --> 00:13:58,200
Showing it to the patient's family

176
00:13:58,279 --> 00:13:59,439
doesn't count as a violation.

177
00:14:08,080 --> 00:14:09,320
When I first met Lu Feng,

178
00:14:09,840 --> 00:14:11,399
he had just started his own company.

179
00:14:12,039 --> 00:14:13,799
He started staying awake all night.

180
00:14:14,519 --> 00:14:15,519
I noticed

181
00:14:15,679 --> 00:14:16,879
he had mild bipolar disorder.

182
00:14:17,200 --> 00:14:18,520
As long as you weren't mentioned,

183
00:14:18,559 --> 00:14:19,959
his condition was mostly manageable

184
00:14:20,519 --> 00:14:22,879
with some simple counseling.

185
00:14:23,480 --> 00:14:24,799
But since he came to Xincheng,

186
00:14:25,639 --> 00:14:27,960
his condition has gotten worse each time.

187
00:14:29,080 --> 00:14:30,560
I've known about you for a long time.

188
00:14:31,039 --> 00:14:32,399
That day, I volunteered

189
00:14:32,679 --> 00:14:34,000
to play the role of his lover.

190
00:14:34,639 --> 00:14:35,799
I just wanted to see

191
00:14:36,080 --> 00:14:37,696
the person who holds
the key to Lu Feng's heart,

192
00:14:37,720 --> 00:14:38,720
and what you were like.

193
00:14:39,960 --> 00:14:41,000
Did I disappoint you?

194
00:14:42,879 --> 00:14:44,159
The fact that you came to see me

195
00:14:45,080 --> 00:14:46,320
means you didn't disappoint me.

196
00:14:48,039 --> 00:14:49,519
How can I help him?

197
00:14:50,240 --> 00:14:51,240
Only you

198
00:14:51,480 --> 00:14:52,759
can make him willing

199
00:14:52,960 --> 00:14:54,400
to go to the hospital for treatment.

200
00:14:54,840 --> 00:14:56,440
Then take me with you guys too.

201
00:14:57,000 --> 00:15:00,160
It's too much trouble, and we don't
really hang out in the same circles anyway.

202
00:15:05,799 --> 00:15:06,799
Yi-chen.

203
00:15:07,480 --> 00:15:08,960
I want to borrow some money from you.

204
00:15:09,559 --> 00:15:10,559
Lu Feng...

205
00:15:13,919 --> 00:15:14,960
He's having some trouble.

206
00:15:22,596 --> 00:15:25,323
[He's checking in with
Yichen, Yichen asks what's up]

207
00:15:31,270 --> 00:15:33,970
[Lu Feng responds with "It's fine"]

208
00:15:48,159 --> 00:15:49,159
Lu Feng.

209
00:15:50,799 --> 00:15:51,799
Come somewhere with me.

210
00:15:58,159 --> 00:15:59,480
I saved up some money myself,

211
00:16:00,000 --> 00:16:01,320
and borrowed some from Yi-chen.

212
00:16:02,919 --> 00:16:05,039
We'll sign the transfer
contract in a couple of days.

213
00:16:05,480 --> 00:16:06,480
From now on,

214
00:16:07,159 --> 00:16:08,240
this will be my home.

215
00:16:12,679 --> 00:16:13,679
Your home?

216
00:16:15,919 --> 00:16:16,919
Lu Feng.

217
00:16:17,720 --> 00:16:18,720
I've been thinking.

218
00:16:19,720 --> 00:16:22,320
We've known each other for over ten years,

219
00:16:22,840 --> 00:16:24,520
and we've been entangled for just as long.

220
00:16:24,879 --> 00:16:26,320
Now, you don't seem like yourself,

221
00:16:27,399 --> 00:16:28,559
and I don't seem like myself.

222
00:16:29,840 --> 00:16:30,840
This...

223
00:16:32,120 --> 00:16:33,240
isn't what I wanted.

224
00:16:35,679 --> 00:16:36,679
From now on,

225
00:16:37,440 --> 00:16:38,720
let's just be friends.

226
00:16:45,240 --> 00:16:46,240
You...

227
00:16:48,600 --> 00:16:50,040
What on earth are you talking about?

228
00:16:52,519 --> 00:16:54,559
Why can't I understand a single word?

229
00:16:56,639 --> 00:16:58,799
Did I do something to make you unhappy?

230
00:17:00,480 --> 00:17:01,480
Or...

231
00:17:02,320 --> 00:17:03,640
are you worried about my illness?

232
00:17:06,359 --> 00:17:08,400
Do you not want to be
with someone who's sick?

233
00:17:16,160 --> 00:17:18,120
If you're sick, why won't
you go to the hospital?

234
00:17:24,240 --> 00:17:25,240
With you like this,

235
00:17:26,279 --> 00:17:27,880
how can I dare to be with you?

236
00:17:30,319 --> 00:17:32,559
Now, there are only two paths left for me.

237
00:17:33,720 --> 00:17:34,720
Either...

238
00:17:35,240 --> 00:17:36,440
we never see each other again,

239
00:17:37,880 --> 00:17:38,880
or...

240
00:17:40,319 --> 00:17:41,480
I die by your hands.

241
00:17:49,400 --> 00:17:51,079
Then let's never see each other again.

242
00:19:16,359 --> 00:19:17,359
Brother.

243
00:19:19,839 --> 00:19:20,839
Brother.

244
00:19:21,039 --> 00:19:22,399
How did Lu Feng suddenly get sick?

245
00:19:22,640 --> 00:19:23,640
You want to buy a house,

246
00:19:23,720 --> 00:19:24,920
and that's because of him too?

247
00:19:27,440 --> 00:19:28,440
His illness...

248
00:19:28,480 --> 00:19:30,821
requires him to rest in an environment
filled with beautiful memories.

249
00:19:31,359 --> 00:19:32,880
That's why I want to buy this house.

250
00:19:33,400 --> 00:19:34,480
I asked you all here today

251
00:19:35,119 --> 00:19:36,640
because I need a favor.

252
00:19:37,200 --> 00:19:38,200
He's sick,

253
00:19:38,680 --> 00:19:40,160
but he refuses to go to the hospital.

254
00:19:40,440 --> 00:19:41,480
I want to ask you guys

255
00:19:42,319 --> 00:19:44,039
to help me force him to go to the hospital.

256
00:19:46,599 --> 00:19:47,279
Yichen.

257
00:19:47,519 --> 00:19:48,519
Actually...

258
00:19:48,640 --> 00:19:49,640
Lu Feng is at the door.

259
00:20:04,440 --> 00:20:05,440
Xiao Chen.

260
00:20:10,279 --> 00:20:11,279
I'm sorry.

261
00:20:13,359 --> 00:20:15,240
I broke your vase.

262
00:20:21,480 --> 00:20:23,640
Give me the glass shards.

263
00:20:38,279 --> 00:20:39,319
Let's go to the hospital.

264
00:20:40,960 --> 00:20:41,960
Okay?

265
00:20:45,039 --> 00:20:46,160
I'm not sick.

266
00:20:52,480 --> 00:20:53,559
I'll go with you.

267
00:20:55,039 --> 00:20:56,039
Okay?

268
00:20:59,119 --> 00:21:01,240
I don't want you to see
me when I have an episode.

269
00:21:02,839 --> 00:21:03,960
No matter what,

270
00:21:05,440 --> 00:21:07,000
I will always stay by your side.

271
00:21:11,519 --> 00:21:12,960
What if my illness

272
00:21:14,720 --> 00:21:15,720
can't be cured?

273
00:21:19,960 --> 00:21:21,480
Will you leave me?

274
00:21:23,599 --> 00:21:24,599
No.

275
00:21:25,680 --> 00:21:26,680
But if...

276
00:21:28,160 --> 00:21:29,279
you don't get treatment,

277
00:21:32,000 --> 00:21:33,400
I will definitely leave you.

278
00:21:41,559 --> 00:21:43,880
What if I have an episode

279
00:21:45,279 --> 00:21:46,880
and I hurt you?

280
00:21:47,359 --> 00:21:48,359
What then?

281
00:21:54,200 --> 00:21:55,880
Then you need treatment even more.

282
00:22:00,839 --> 00:22:02,400
What if it can't be cured?

283
00:22:05,119 --> 00:22:06,119
Then I'll...

284
00:22:07,759 --> 00:22:09,079
go crazy with you.

285
00:22:31,319 --> 00:22:32,480
Bipolar disorder.

286
00:22:32,599 --> 00:22:33,400
Generally speaking,

287
00:22:33,480 --> 00:22:35,640
it's just a glitch in the
brain's emotional switch.

288
00:22:35,880 --> 00:22:37,495
Don't let the information online scare you.

289
00:22:37,519 --> 00:22:39,559
This condition is completely manageable.

290
00:22:40,200 --> 00:22:41,880
So what should I do?

291
00:22:42,880 --> 00:22:43,880
Just cooperate with me.

292
00:23:09,400 --> 00:23:11,640
Do you really have to leave in a bit?

293
00:23:15,240 --> 00:23:16,240
Once I'm cured,

294
00:23:16,720 --> 00:23:18,720
you won't leave me again, right?

295
00:23:24,799 --> 00:23:26,319
Can't you stay with me?

296
00:23:27,079 --> 00:23:28,079
No.

297
00:23:28,279 --> 00:23:29,319
Dr. Zhao won't allow it.

298
00:24:43,240 --> 00:24:44,240
Yichen.

299
00:24:57,599 --> 00:24:59,559
I used to think you two were
just young and reckless,

300
00:25:00,559 --> 00:25:01,880
not knowing how the world works,

301
00:25:02,759 --> 00:25:04,400
thinking love conquers all.

302
00:25:05,319 --> 00:25:06,720
Now you're in your thirties,

303
00:25:07,400 --> 00:25:08,400
and yet, because of love,

304
00:25:08,640 --> 00:25:10,360
you've driven yourselves to mental illness.

305
00:25:11,599 --> 00:25:12,799
He's really something.

306
00:25:13,880 --> 00:25:15,039
He will get better.

307
00:25:21,720 --> 00:25:22,920
Leave the company to me.

308
00:25:23,519 --> 00:25:25,519
I'll leave Lu Feng to you.

309
00:25:28,480 --> 00:25:29,480
Yichen.

310
00:25:30,359 --> 00:25:31,359
Thank you.

311
00:25:31,640 --> 00:25:32,720
You don't need to thank me.

312
00:25:33,640 --> 00:25:34,799
He's my family too.

313
00:25:51,079 --> 00:25:53,000
I don't want to take my medicine right now.

314
00:25:53,119 --> 00:25:54,799
I want to see Cheng Yichen.

315
00:26:05,960 --> 00:26:07,440
- I want to see Xiao Chen.
- Mr. Lu...

316
00:26:08,319 --> 00:26:08,920
Mr. Lu.

317
00:26:08,921 --> 00:26:10,160
- Xiao Chen...
- I'm here.

318
00:26:10,480 --> 00:26:11,558
- Mr. Lu...
- Xiao Chen.

319
00:26:11,559 --> 00:26:12,598
Take your medicine first, Mr. Lu.

320
00:26:12,599 --> 00:26:13,880
Xiao Chen.

321
00:27:18,839 --> 00:27:19,839
Thank you.

322
00:29:48,400 --> 00:29:49,400
Lu Feng.

323
00:29:50,720 --> 00:29:51,920
I'm here to take you home.

324
00:30:09,799 --> 00:30:11,400
The first person to study in a bar.

325
00:30:12,039 --> 00:30:13,039
Shut up.

326
00:30:13,480 --> 00:30:14,480
How cute.

327
00:30:14,799 --> 00:30:16,679
He wants to go to grad
school for architecture.

328
00:30:18,720 --> 00:30:19,960
That's really impressive.

329
00:30:20,079 --> 00:30:21,079
Of course.

330
00:30:25,480 --> 00:30:26,480
Bullshit.

331
00:30:40,000 --> 00:30:41,040
For his ongoing condition,

332
00:30:41,079 --> 00:30:42,480
you'll need to monitor him closely.

333
00:30:43,279 --> 00:30:44,976
Besides making sure he
takes his medicine on time,

334
00:30:45,000 --> 00:30:46,240
try to keep him in

335
00:30:46,519 --> 00:30:49,000
a relatively peaceful and
stable home environment.

336
00:30:49,319 --> 00:30:50,319
As for work,

337
00:30:50,440 --> 00:30:52,079
avoid any intense arguments.

338
00:30:52,720 --> 00:30:54,119
Okay, don't worry.

339
00:30:54,240 --> 00:30:55,240
I'll keep that in mind.

340
00:30:56,400 --> 00:30:57,400
Are you hungry?

341
00:30:58,119 --> 00:30:59,119
Not really.

342
00:30:59,559 --> 00:31:01,640
What do you want for dinner?

343
00:31:01,880 --> 00:31:03,079
I want to eat...

344
00:31:04,880 --> 00:31:06,040
the instant noodles you make.

345
00:31:08,720 --> 00:31:09,720
Lu Feng.

346
00:31:10,200 --> 00:31:11,200
Now that you're cured,

347
00:31:11,720 --> 00:31:12,720
aren't you happy?

348
00:31:14,440 --> 00:31:15,559
I am happy.

349
00:31:17,160 --> 00:31:18,960
I haven't been this happy in years.

350
00:31:19,519 --> 00:31:21,480
I can finally be with
you without any worries.

351
00:31:23,119 --> 00:31:24,400
I'm so happy

352
00:31:24,799 --> 00:31:26,799
that I don't even know what to do.

353
00:31:28,200 --> 00:31:29,720
But you look

354
00:31:30,000 --> 00:31:31,480
a bit unhappy.

355
00:31:34,279 --> 00:31:37,480
Ever since I started
waiting for you this morning,

356
00:31:38,519 --> 00:31:39,799
I kept telling myself

357
00:31:40,759 --> 00:31:42,200
that I must show you

358
00:31:43,119 --> 00:31:45,200
an incredibly happy face.

359
00:31:46,160 --> 00:31:47,160
That way,

360
00:31:47,599 --> 00:31:48,799
you'll feel at ease.

361
00:31:50,400 --> 00:31:51,519
But I realized

362
00:31:53,359 --> 00:31:55,599
I don't know what happiness looks like,

363
00:31:56,920 --> 00:31:57,960
nor do I know

364
00:31:59,039 --> 00:32:00,599
what kind of face to make.

365
00:32:06,720 --> 00:32:07,880
Lu Feng, look.

366
00:32:08,640 --> 00:32:09,640
Just like this.

367
00:32:21,640 --> 00:32:22,640
We'll take it

368
00:32:23,119 --> 00:32:24,119
one step at a time,

369
00:32:24,240 --> 00:32:25,240
okay?

370
00:32:39,519 --> 00:32:41,319
Why do you still keep this?

371
00:32:59,599 --> 00:33:00,599
Close your eyes.

372
00:34:29,960 --> 00:34:31,079
Love...

373
00:34:31,480 --> 00:34:32,655
It moves people, but it hurts them too.

374
00:34:32,679 --> 00:34:34,320
Look at you, getting all poetic.

375
00:34:35,400 --> 00:34:36,719
Good thing I'm easygoing.

376
00:34:36,840 --> 00:34:37,599
Otherwise,

377
00:34:37,719 --> 00:34:39,256
I would've been driven
sick by you long ago.

378
00:34:39,280 --> 00:34:40,960
Then should I thank you

379
00:34:41,239 --> 00:34:42,799
for putting up with me all these years?

380
00:34:44,000 --> 00:34:45,200
How are you going to thank me?

381
00:34:48,559 --> 00:34:49,559
There are people here.

382
00:34:49,880 --> 00:34:51,159
So what if there are?

383
00:36:53,400 --> 00:36:54,840
Why are you looking at me like that?

384
00:36:57,320 --> 00:36:59,320
I'm so happy, it feels like a dream.

385
00:37:02,480 --> 00:37:03,480
How about now?

386
00:37:06,480 --> 00:37:07,760
Now it feels even more like one.

387
00:37:14,119 --> 00:37:15,119
From now on,

388
00:37:15,400 --> 00:37:17,880
we will be very, very happy forever.

389
00:38:05,800 --> 00:38:06,800
Lu Feng.

390
00:38:07,440 --> 00:38:08,440
Lu Feng.

391
00:38:20,320 --> 00:38:21,559
Lu Feng.

392
00:38:25,000 --> 00:38:26,000
Lu Feng.

393
00:38:26,320 --> 00:38:28,079
Lu Feng.

394
00:38:28,880 --> 00:38:29,880
Lu Feng.

395
00:38:32,519 --> 00:38:33,519
Xiao Chen.

396
00:38:36,559 --> 00:38:37,559
Xiao Chen.

397
00:38:37,719 --> 00:38:38,719
Xiao Chen.

398
00:38:39,159 --> 00:38:40,480
Did you have a nightmare?

399
00:38:46,360 --> 00:38:47,400
Lu Feng,

400
00:38:48,960 --> 00:38:50,599
I had a dream.

401
00:38:53,880 --> 00:38:54,880
What kind of dream?

402
00:38:54,960 --> 00:38:56,000
I dreamed...

403
00:38:58,559 --> 00:39:00,559
Your illness was never cured,

404
00:39:02,840 --> 00:39:04,000
and then,

405
00:39:08,760 --> 00:39:10,239
without saying a word,

406
00:39:12,800 --> 00:39:14,000
you just died.

407
00:39:15,880 --> 00:39:16,920
How could that happen?

408
00:39:19,000 --> 00:39:20,000
Don't worry.

409
00:39:22,480 --> 00:39:24,400
I would never leave

410
00:39:25,239 --> 00:39:26,800
and die without telling you.

411
00:39:29,639 --> 00:39:30,639
That was just a dream.

412
00:39:32,000 --> 00:39:34,079
I'm going to live a very long life,

413
00:39:36,800 --> 00:39:38,000
just as long as you.

414
00:39:40,639 --> 00:39:42,800
Actually, I want to live longer than you.

415
00:39:42,960 --> 00:39:43,960
Just by a little bit.

416
00:39:45,320 --> 00:39:46,320
That way,

417
00:39:47,960 --> 00:39:49,800
you won't be left all alone in this world,

418
00:39:50,639 --> 00:39:52,119
and you won't have to feel that pain.

419
00:39:58,840 --> 00:39:59,840
Xiao Chen.

420
00:40:06,480 --> 00:40:07,559
From now on,

421
00:40:09,119 --> 00:40:10,519
things will only get better for us.

422
00:40:32,639 --> 00:40:33,719
Time to wake up!

423
00:40:36,599 --> 00:40:37,199
Lu Feng.

424
00:40:37,480 --> 00:40:38,480
Lu Feng!

425
00:40:38,800 --> 00:40:40,800
What is it so early in the morning?

426
00:40:41,559 --> 00:40:42,559
Lu Feng,

427
00:40:47,480 --> 00:40:48,880
you've gotten so cute.

428
00:40:52,119 --> 00:40:53,119
Me too.

429
00:40:53,320 --> 00:40:55,599
It's been so long since
I've seen you this energetic.

430
00:40:56,440 --> 00:40:57,440
It's just like

431
00:40:57,840 --> 00:40:59,079
back when we were in school.

432
00:41:00,360 --> 00:41:02,800
Well, look who's to blame for that.

433
00:41:03,039 --> 00:41:04,719
If you let me be on top

434
00:41:05,519 --> 00:41:06,519
every day from now on,

435
00:41:06,760 --> 00:41:08,360
I promise I'll always be full of energy.

436
00:41:14,360 --> 00:41:15,400
If

437
00:41:16,119 --> 00:41:17,480
that's really what you want,

438
00:41:20,000 --> 00:41:21,560
I suppose it's not out of the question.

439
00:41:22,199 --> 00:41:23,199
Really?

440
00:41:32,039 --> 00:41:33,039
If only

441
00:41:33,719 --> 00:41:35,039
you were only this small,

442
00:41:36,239 --> 00:41:37,359
how wonderful that would be.

443
00:41:38,159 --> 00:41:39,800
I could just slip you into my pocket,

444
00:41:40,480 --> 00:41:41,480
and wherever I go,

445
00:41:42,360 --> 00:41:43,400
I could take you with me.

446
00:41:44,960 --> 00:41:45,960
That way, I could see you

447
00:41:46,559 --> 00:41:47,559
anytime I want.

448
00:41:47,599 --> 00:41:49,199
What a coincidence.

449
00:41:49,719 --> 00:41:53,400
I used to wish I could
shrink you down like that, too.

450
00:41:54,199 --> 00:41:55,000
And then what?

451
00:41:55,199 --> 00:41:56,559
Put you in my bag,

452
00:41:56,920 --> 00:41:58,880
so that from then on,

453
00:42:00,079 --> 00:42:01,319
I could always bring you along.

454
00:42:09,639 --> 00:42:12,960
Then find a good spot

455
00:42:13,880 --> 00:42:15,000
to put me in.

456
00:42:15,880 --> 00:42:16,880
Wherever you go,

457
00:42:18,519 --> 00:42:19,559
I'll follow.

458
00:42:20,199 --> 00:42:21,199
How childish.

459
00:42:27,760 --> 00:42:28,760
Thank you, thank you!

460
00:42:28,960 --> 00:42:29,360
Bye-bye!

461
00:42:29,361 --> 00:42:31,081
See? I told you he has a mind for business.

462
00:42:32,440 --> 00:42:33,440
Where's your brother?

463
00:42:33,519 --> 00:42:36,000
He should be at the airport by now.

464
00:42:36,679 --> 00:42:37,880
Why didn't you go see him off?

465
00:42:39,159 --> 00:42:40,159
Better not.

466
00:42:40,519 --> 00:42:41,599
I'm afraid if I went,

467
00:42:41,719 --> 00:42:43,719
I'd make a scene and try
to stop him from leaving.

468
00:42:45,800 --> 00:42:46,880
So, from now on,

469
00:42:47,280 --> 00:42:49,320
you plan to run this shop with Xiao Lo?

470
00:42:51,239 --> 00:42:51,960
Yeah.

471
00:42:52,239 --> 00:42:53,999
We're going to turn
it into a national chain

472
00:42:54,079 --> 00:42:55,079
and take it public.

473
00:42:55,719 --> 00:42:56,719
When that happens,

474
00:42:57,440 --> 00:42:58,440
I'll take care of you.

475
00:42:59,159 --> 00:43:00,359
Who needs you to take of me?

476
00:43:02,360 --> 00:43:03,360
Lu Feng,

477
00:43:04,199 --> 00:43:05,639
besides doing business,

478
00:43:06,039 --> 00:43:07,559
what do you want to do most right now?

479
00:43:08,239 --> 00:43:09,239
I don't know.

480
00:43:11,719 --> 00:43:13,159
I just want to be with you.

481
00:43:15,199 --> 00:43:16,400
Let me rephrase that.

482
00:43:17,000 --> 00:43:18,000
Right now,

483
00:43:18,559 --> 00:43:19,679
what do you want to do most?

484
00:43:21,559 --> 00:43:22,719
Right now?

485
00:43:24,679 --> 00:43:25,880
I want to go back to the past.

486
00:43:26,039 --> 00:43:27,760
We really love your short videos!

487
00:43:27,880 --> 00:43:28,320
Yeah, we do!

488
00:43:28,320 --> 00:43:29,079
Thank you.

489
00:43:29,199 --> 00:43:30,599
We came here straight after school.

490
00:43:31,039 --> 00:43:31,840
Keep it up!

491
00:43:32,039 --> 00:43:33,175
Can we take a photo together?

492
00:43:33,199 --> 00:43:34,360
Sure, of course.

493
00:43:34,480 --> 00:43:35,840
I guess we could.

494
00:43:35,920 --> 00:43:37,360
Thank you so much!

495
00:43:37,440 --> 00:43:38,440
No problem.

496
00:43:44,039 --> 00:43:44,760
Give me a push.

497
00:43:44,760 --> 00:43:45,760
Okay.

498
00:43:49,239 --> 00:43:51,239
If you're not going to use
your eyes, donate them!

499
00:43:57,039 --> 00:43:57,800
Forget it, forget it.

500
00:43:58,000 --> 00:43:59,000
Let's go.

501
00:43:59,119 --> 00:44:00,119
Hurry up.

502
00:44:08,639 --> 00:44:10,760
Fortune telling!

503
00:44:11,119 --> 00:44:13,960
Career, marriage, I read it all!

504
00:44:16,159 --> 00:44:17,800
Palmistry and face reading!

505
00:44:18,000 --> 00:44:19,480
No charge if it's not accurate!

506
00:44:20,440 --> 00:44:22,000
Guaranteed accuracy!

507
00:44:22,280 --> 00:44:24,159
One reading to reveal your destiny!

508
00:44:27,960 --> 00:44:29,239
Give me your hand.

509
00:44:39,559 --> 00:44:41,159
Let me calculate...

510
00:44:41,400 --> 00:44:42,440
In this life,

511
00:44:42,599 --> 00:44:44,239
your path of love is full of obstacles.

512
00:44:44,719 --> 00:44:45,960
All your life,

513
00:44:46,239 --> 00:44:49,079
you'll be entangled with men.

514
00:44:50,000 --> 00:44:51,960
And...

515
00:44:57,679 --> 00:44:58,719
Hey, you haven't paid yet!

516
00:45:05,639 --> 00:45:06,360
And...

517
00:45:06,519 --> 00:45:08,239
it will always be with the same man.

518
00:45:08,400 --> 00:45:11,800
But though the road of love is winding,

519
00:45:12,360 --> 00:45:16,159
true lovers will find their happy ending.

520
00:45:18,239 --> 00:45:19,239
Really?

521
00:45:19,320 --> 00:45:20,400
Thank you, Master.

522
00:45:22,360 --> 00:45:23,800
Come on, let's go home.

523
00:45:24,239 --> 00:45:27,000
Wait, I wasn't wrong!
